snippet.title: Scrappers, OUT NOW on Apple Arcade!
snippet.description:
Trash and smash your way through the city streets as one part of a robotic city cleanup crew out for a big payday, while junking punks who try to stop them!
Play by yourself or with up to three other friends, over couch-coop or online multiplayer! Full Xbox and PlayStation controller and MFI support on a single device!
Available on iPhone, iPad, iPod touch, Apple TV and Mac.

https://apps.apple.com/app/scrappers/id1464109659
